    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He ordained our days to start in this way,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We clearly see in the creation of man—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The first day of man was the seventh day,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To enjoy God’s presence, ere he worked on the land."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In our time it is the same,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "This divine principle remains..."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "First we need to rest, just to lay down,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "This is what God wants, before the work abounds."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "First enjoy the Lord! Just drink Him in."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Once we’re filled with Him—let the work begin."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "chorus"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "So begin your day reclining on Him,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Enjoying Him as the pleasant pasture land,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Sing until He overflows from the brim,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Flowing out from you to reach whoever’s at hand."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "If you first behold His face,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Your labor will be done by grace!"
            }
          ]
        }
